{"tid":419309,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[真理] 終於明點解長賭必輸 想戒賭就入","createTime":"2017-09-30T11:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T14:33:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":25,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"80d9b52157e1bf44ba65bdaba19b3568320d0614","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>1. 用邏輯去解釋長賭必輸</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果賭博係公平 賭場 馬會 股票市場就唔會存在<br />\n<br />\n佢地存在係因為 隻game本身set到莊係贏多d 當6成 而其他人得4成機會羸<br />\n<br />\n遊戲設計再set到隻game好玩 令賭仔沉迷<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係賭仔輸咁多錢 賭場邊有錢請人 交租 交水電 <br />\n<br />\n否則 賭場就會消失<br />\n<br />\nprove by contradiction, 而家賭場, 馬會, 股票市場係存在, 證明長賭係必輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 用統計學解釋長賭必輸</strong><br />\n<br />\n所有賭錢game都係負和遊戲 所得少於所失<br />\n<br />\n圍骰又好 衍生工具又好 六合彩又好 都係負和遊戲 <br />\n<br />\n做莊一定羸 隻隻game都有人計好晒數 再擺起賭場比人玩<br />\n<br />\n同樣假設有隻負和遊戲有4成機會比你贏 <br />\n<br />\n就當你第一次落場賭 比你好彩羸左 一般賭仔就會有癮去長賭<br />\n<br />\n如果長賭落去 姐係等於要你keep住用呢4成機會日日去搏<br />\n<br />\n再當你有無限日子去賭 每日4成機會 你會發現你好快會輸晒d錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 連牛頓咁聰明都賭輸錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n我當有人聰明到好似牛頓咁 可以將羸的機會提高<br />\n<br />\n不過事實上係 就算牛頓佢係好聰明 <br />\n<br />\n佢都唔能夠將贏的機會提高到長賭不輸<br />\n<br />\n所以 原來長賭真係必輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論</strong><br />\n<br />\n長賭係必輸 我成套想法未必完整 <br />\n<br />\n例如你可以駁我話 可能10個天才 有9個係靠賭發達 牛頓咁岩唔好彩姐<br />\n<br />\n其實要拗就大把野可以拗 <br />\n<br />\n不過 拗羸我冇意思<br />\n<br />\n因為更有意思係呢套想法至少可以幫倒一部分人戒賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦至少說服倒我自己去戒賭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想做個小統計<br />\n<br />\n如果你地賭左咁多年都係輸錢既就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你地賭左咁多年都有錢羸既就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310ce9b7c1e86ffada2e731ba4c1f220718be86d","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔好信啲咩期望值只係少少負嘅說話，一個人黑起上嚟真係好癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f23738ab06a86390b73fe88656b7f44bf1125","tid":419309,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:31:23.000Z","msg":"買大細點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf6c0d4e43691368edee2d26c0032c998876206","tid":419309,"uid":142433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6334407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6334407&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4qS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=0482c5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6334407</a>"},{"pid":"33678828ffbb68f053f3a3f4fdfb3f4dcc240315","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"好簡單 <br />\n一場賭局 <br />\n就算賭場同賭仔,贏嘅機會均等 <br />\n唔好好忘記,仲要抽水 <br />\n姐係你羸嘅期望值,已經係負數 <br />\n<br />\n如果你信統計學 <br />\n只要賭得越多,就會越接近賭場定出黎嘅期望值 <br />\n呢個期望值,對你黎講一定係負數 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔想去到呢個負期望值,就賭少幾局 <br />\n最好就只玩一局 <br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野,唔好以為贏嘅機會率低少少(e.g. 0.5-1%),就以為好少 <br />\n其實,玩多幾局個影響就好大 <br />\n<br />\n總結:去賭場,我建議,首先決定自己可以用幾多錢 <br />\n然後一炮過,用哂你嘅預算,贏輸都要走"},{"pid":"61445dd13d00354233a43f16161234b872918376","tid":419309,"uid":2655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6334407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6334407&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4qS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=0482c5f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6334407</a></blockquote><br />\n抄post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df963382326981c0e97dcbc1be81de6c0e28918","tid":419309,"uid":27608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買大細點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇聽過通殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d679ff79493cdbb2386af98087bc59164528cdd3","tid":419309,"uid":27608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買大細點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇聽過通殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a1168f474a2cb18c772e6d4389d3a8d53a4624","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"賭仔心理<br />\n幾時有賭仔會覺得自己輸?<br />\n佢理得你賭大細既期望值?<br />\n就算大細1賠1.8, 甚至1.7都大把人賭<br />\n因為賭仔 1)覺得自己會估中 2)賭博刺激<br />\n大細呢D咁隨機既野賭仔都會對自己充滿信心<br />\n更唔洗講賭波賭馬呢D有得&quot;捉路&quot;既賭 <br />\n就算賠率係高定低都好, 賭仔只係會將自己勝率放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b637f9498f9cac3bae5309ca2df4fe0bb02df74c","tid":419309,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"樓主打字都幾撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dc8b7d88a92381bea54d752cc09b764a316fd5","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:34:36.000Z","msg":"除咗 長賭必輸 之外 <br />\n本多終勝 又係另一大道理 <br />\n由於賭哂就無得玩 <br />\n賭本越多,可以承受短期嘅大量損失 <br />\n令你成功可以賭到好多好多局 <br />\n從而去達賭局中嘅期望值 <br />\n賭本少,好快用哂,好易無得玩落去"},{"pid":"27880563f3edb372a6bf603a2f28dbc3a751c815","tid":419309,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"信左 樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直係救世主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a953f88668ac06433ffaee85bb1784b81542b05d","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"以前有位玩德樸發達既高手(依家好似去左搞app)接受雜誌訪問講過，要賭就一定唔好掂同賭場對賭或者純粹賭運既遊戲，人地計好晒數，點賭都係突破唔到數學規律，要賭一定係玩剩係同人對賭既遊戲，有得憑自己技術同心理戰去贏"},{"pid":"0a7b0771f145600c64998d9e9ff43b9d4c6fb592","tid":419309,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"因為你只係識隨機咁賭。<br />\n咁個賠率有負期望值係計隨機。<br />\n如果你可以統計出各項參數係點樣左右到個結果。<br />\n你就會長嬴。<br />\n<br />\n21點計牌<br />\n輪盤計物理<br />\n賭馬睇參數<br />\n<br />\n有人會長嬴，但果類人好聰明，同埋唔係你我而矣。"},{"pid":"0db233181980fcb85c27becbc4bca691d4616f3d","tid":419309,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"睇返樓主開過既po先明白乜野叫學識淵博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598d6ccdd36ad788e389da2850e8d11037d17b29","tid":419309,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"有教授寫賭馬程式<br />\n可以贏錢喎"},{"pid":"8f6cf24da48e7e5791a5e833fdc8fbbb893574de","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"Gambling is a tax on the poor and stupid <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凡係賭場做莊 數學上長遠你無可能win<br />\n差1%就係1% 賭場咁多人 背後成堆友仔砌哂model 計過哂機率 你以為你叻過友仔?<br />\n除非你有超能力 Or 出術 否則只係自取滅亡<br />\n<br />\n要有錢搵 <br />\n只能夠向blackjack埋手 但賭場近幾十年見過哂你D人點玩<br />\nD漏點都封得七七八八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都無乜肉食<br />\n<br />\n一係就賭場無做莊既texas hold'em<br />\n賭仔同賭仔對賭就ok<br />\n<br />\n百家樂個D 你當老虎機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407f10ca6b41591fb207b8f553446b3e9cbce1a4","tid":419309,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"這些贏率計算有一個前提，那就是小球停在哪個格子是隨機的。這一點並非很容易做到。比如1873年，有玩家對蒙特卡羅大賭場的輪盤賭進行了五個星期的細緻觀察，結果發現了系統偏差，並因此贏得了約65000英鎊&mdash;&mdash;在當時是不小的數目。不過，只要製作和調試足夠仔細，系統偏差是能被有效除去的。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/48vmo52.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2F48vmo52.html&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4qS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=0b3b3d5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/48vmo52.html</a><br />\n<br />\n當然一百年後，輪盤都已經「改良」左好多了。<br />\n所以依家係用電腦黎計物理。"},{"pid":"74808b483ed102f42c4861e13f9bf51d7981a215","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:40:41.000Z","msg":"賭場每張枱賭既野既expected value都係對賭場有利, 佢唔怕你贏錢最緊要你坐得耐. 所以有免費野飲, 贏大錢送你一晚suite又如何"},{"pid":"bb346b5e347f0bd91b54665c67f6a083a2a04103","tid":419309,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有教授寫賭馬程式<br />\n可以贏錢喎</blockquote><br />\n咪又係-6"},{"pid":"de2c90bd6c9cc62d85a72bfc68577554ddce1209","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"我記得有本書講過， <br />\n要長賭既話，只有百家樂係有機會贏錢 <br />\n當然呢個「長」係算式上既infinity啦...或者係「足夠長」嘅次數... <br />\n其他係必輸... <br />\n<br />\n但，只係算式上。"},{"pid":"b2a6dc7740bfcdeec04d54f3a28a0059a7296bff","tid":419309,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得有本書講過， <br />\n要長賭既話，只有百家樂係有機會贏錢 <br />\n當然呢個「長」係算式上既infinity啦...或者係「足夠長」嘅次數... <br />\n其他係必輸... <br />\n<br />\n但，只係算式上。</blockquote><br />\n記你老母咩扮大袋 你機械人黎咋"},{"pid":"3ac03d4cdeac8cc0612be14f8ebca8fd6c65c6ec","tid":419309,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有教授寫賭馬程式<br />\n可以贏錢喎</blockquote><br />\n咪又係-6</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都痴痴地。<br />\n人地每日有幾萬個交易<br />\n已經係「長賭」<br />\n重要賭左幾年。"},{"pid":"924862519599d4e0fd0c9815166942aaed3b3730","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"賭馬比起賭場難估好多 <br />\n馬同人始終都係生物,難估計,賭馬嘅倍率,馬會有可能定錯,教授就會贏錢 <br />\n但賭場真係純數學遊戲好難會錯"},{"pid":"02e9e09975ab6f1e3b148f1e5f52c3c6a09c682c","tid":419309,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以下d 文字同內容甚至youtube片都係出至一個宗教團體既報導,但整件事我覺得完全同呢個宗教無關,佢地只係報導左呢單新聞,然後加入自己宗教既見解,所以入面有d涉及宗教內容,請自行分辨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一套50多年前出版的著名童書《Berenstein Bears》， <br />\n不知從何時開始，所有相關資訊， <br />\n包括互聯網，甚至人們珍藏的書本上， <br />\n本來印刷了的書名，突然一律如魔法般，變成《Berenstain Bears》！ <br />\n<br />\n這事令人費解，甚至接近「靈異」事件， <br />\n掀起了一連串的網上討論。 <br />\n<br />\n當你了解來龍去脈以後， <br />\n你會驚覺，我們以為牢固的現實世界 <br />\n原來，竟是這麼脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n意思是，假如一天你睡醒後，<br />\n你記憶之中的多啦A夢，變成了多啦B夢，<br />\n你會覺得恐怖嗎？<br />\n但現實中，就正正發生著這麼恐怖的事... ... <br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-UDOTpchL8FI/VY_ZS6HLMqI/AAAAAAAADz0/kxxTlcsJQ9w/s1600/BerenstainBears_crop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-UDOTpchL8FI%2FVY_ZS6HLMqI%2FAAAAAAAADz0%2FkxxTlcsJQ9w%2Fs1600%2FBerenstainBears_crop.jpg&h=0649bcc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe Berenstein Bears，一套於美國非常著名的兒童圖書。 Berenstein Bears，由 Stan 及 Jan Berenstein 所創作， 由 1962 年開始，出版第一本兒童圖書，至今已超過 50 年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-7q_I86LKCaw/VY_tofFCneI/AAAAAAAAD0E/dq3eLniYHsE/s1600/001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-7q_I86LKCaw%2FVY_tofFCneI%2FAAAAAAAAD0E%2Fdq3eLniYHsE%2Fs1600%2F001.jpg&h=d1e2696b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBerenstein Bears 是很多人的童年回憶，它的讀物亦是很多人的收藏之一。 <br />\n<br />\n甚至在無數個晚上，很多父母都會把它的讀物，當作牀邊故事，哄小孩入睡。 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但不知何時開始，Berenstein Bears 的所有資訊、珍藏書本，<br />\n甚至互聯網， 都不再是 Berenstein Bears 這個名字，突然變了 Berenstain Bears， <br />\n由「stein」s-t-e-i-n，變為「stain」s-t-a-i-n。</span><br />\n<br />\n 這實在是一件十分奇怪，令人難以理解的事情。 <br />\n甚至連官方網站，也變成了 Berenstain Bears。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gWBfdFPUqZg/VY_tzpCh19I/AAAAAAAAD0M/4sx6OFBYeV4/s1600/002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-gWBfdFPUqZg%2FVY_tzpCh19I%2FAAAAAAAAD0M%2F4sx6OFBYeV4%2Fs1600%2F002.jpg&h=5350a5e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你於 YouTube 網站，輸入&ldquo;Berestein Bears&rdquo;搜尋，<br />\n你會發現，很多片段的名稱是&ldquo;Berestein Bears&rdquo;，<br />\ns-t-e-i-n 但內容卻是&ldquo;Berestain Bears&rdquo;，s-t-a-i-n。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hJSb7VF2oTY/VY_t_cI6S2I/AAAAAAAAD0U/4NKUVDhZkBU/s1600/003.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-hJSb7VF2oTY%2FVY_t_cI6S2I%2FAAAAAAAAD0U%2F4NKUVDhZkBU%2Fs1600%2F003.jpg&h=41bc32d3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}